<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        /* Inline styles for maximum compatibility */
        .email-layout {
            max-width: 414px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-footer {
            max-width: 414px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Helvetica;
        }

        .image-container {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .listing-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 240px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 0px;
            border: 0.29px #D9D9D9 solid;
            margin-top: 10px
        }

        .header-1 {
            color: #193666;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .subheader-1 {
            color: #282828;
            font-weight: 200;
        }

        .header-2 {
            color: #009999;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .location {
            font-weight: 300;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 414px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .body {
            font-family: Helvetica;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            height: fit-content;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        footer {
            max-width: 414px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow-x: visible;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 0px;
            border: 0.29px #D9D9D9 solid;
            margin-top: 10px
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table class="email-layout">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <img src="https://spacepal-email-assets-prd.s3.amazonaws.com/footer.png" alt="spacePal" border="0"
                        width="auto" height="70" style="margin-left: -30px;  margin-bottom: -20px;">
                    <h2 class="subheader-1"><strong>Recibiste un pago</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img class="listing-image" src="{{imageUrl.path}}" />
                    </div>
                    <div style="border:1px solid #D9D9D9; border-radius: 5px; padding-left: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">
                        <h4 class="header-2" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">{{spaceTitle}}</h4>
                        <p class="location" tyle="margin-top: 0px;">
                            <span>
                                <img src="https://spacepal-email-assets-prd.s3.amazonaws.com/location.png"
                                    height="15px" width="auto" style="margin-right: 5px;" />
                            </span>
                            <span>
                                {{spaceLocation}}
                            </span>
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            {{date}}
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Total: {{payment}}
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <p>
                        El mail que te gusta: ¡Recibiste un pago! <br /> {{guest}} ya pagó su reserva, clave.
                        Acordate que vas a recibir tu pago en hasta 5 días hábiles en tu cuenta bancaria.
                    <p>

                        <br />
                        <br />
                    <div>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/spacepalar/" target="_blank"
                            style="text-decoration: none; margin-right: 10px;">
                            <img src="https://spacepal-email-assets-prd.s3.amazonaws.com/linkedin-icon" alt="linkedin"
                                border="0" width="20" height="20">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/spacepal.ar/" target="_blank"
                            style="text-decoration: none; margin-right: 10px;">
                            <img src="https://spacepal-email-assets-prd.s3.amazonaws.com/instagram-icon"
                                alt="instagram" border="0" width="20" height="20">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@spacepal.pro" target="_blank"
                            style="text-decoration: none;  margin-right: 10px;">
                            <img src=" https://spacepal-email-assets-prd.s3.amazonaws.com/Tiktok+icon" alt="instagram"
                                border="0" width="20" height="20">
                        </a>

                    </div>
                    <div style='width: 100%; height: 0px; border: 0.29px #D9D9D9 solid; margin-top:10px'>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Libertad para trabajar desde donde quieras.
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 12px;">
                        En caso de una duda contáctese con support@space-pal.com
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
